ComicInfo.Summary:
Whose Face Is at My Window?: Don Nolan rushes home to save his wife from a deranged killer.
The UFO from Planet Earth: Two Air Force captains are sent to investigate strange UFO sightings.
Weave a Tangled Skein of Death: Jason Forbes attempts to steal a tapestry from the Cult of Korex.
Snake Fright: Mr. Pinkney does not like his neighbor or his pet snakes.
Deadly Homecoming!: Vanessa's boyfriend and his fellow soldier return from Vietnam carrying the spirit of Omani, god of war.
